title: Mysterious Midwest Parnormal Series By Munroe Falls Paranormal S
description:
Mysterious Midwest Parnormal Series By Munroe Falls Paranormal Society (MFPS) (2009-2010) mp4s


Another Ghost hunting team.. but some great editing and stories and evidence


loved the GHOST in the car one.. but havent watch any really yet


well worth having in your paranormal collections


I left them as MP4s to keep the quality. 

however they could be better quality. the first 4 they didnt normalize the audio

from studio to the evidence and interviews.. but its minor.. turn up the audio a bit

so aspects were wrong.. and I see some pixelling.. perhaps its was the strsaming site
creating some of the problems/errors

but overall its very clear video.. 400p or better 

each episode goes from 20min to 1 hour
